cff-version: 1.2.0
title: Competitive Intelligence Prompts
message: "If you use this prompt library, please cite it using these metadata."
type: dataset
authors:
  - name: IntelCue
    website: "https://www.intelcue.ai"
repository-code: "https://github.com/IntelCue/competitive-intelligence-prompts"
url: "https://github.com/IntelCue/competitive-intelligence-prompts"
abstract: >-
  An open-source, copy-paste prompt library for competitive intelligence,
  competitor analysis, market intelligence, market research, SEO analysis,
  and competitive monitoring. The prompts are model-agnostic and work with
  ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, and other large language models.
keywords:
  - competitive intelligence
  - market intelligence
  - competitor analysis
  - market research
  - competitive monitoring
  - prompts
  - large language models
  - artificial intelligence
license: MIT
